x <- seq(0, 3, by = .1)
isolinear <- function(s, p) 1 - (1 - s / p)
isogaussian <- function(s, p) 1 - exp(-(s / p)^2)
isoraquad <- function(s, p) (s / p)^2 / (1 + (s / p)^2)
